        document.getElementById("langs-text-aboutmetext4-2").innerHTML = `Besides projects for real clients, my portfolio also includes my personal projects that I often work on in my free time. Their primary purpose is learning new skills and software, while also improving in what I already know.`
        document.getElementById("langs-text-aboutmetext4-3").innerHTML = `As a supporter of open source software, I often like to make use of such tools in my projects and I also use Fedora Linux as my primary system. However, I have no problem with using industry standard software as well, which I still work with most of the time.`
        document.getElementById("langs-text-aboutmetitle3").innerHTML = `What's next`
